<h2 style="color: #1A1A1A; margin-top: 0;">Order Confirmed!</h2>

<p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>

<p>Thank you for your order! We are pleased to confirm that your order has been received and is being processed.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><span class="label">Order Number:</span> {{orderNumber}}</p>
  <p><span class="label">Order ID:</span> {{orderId}}</p>
  {{#if orderDate}}
  <p><span class="label">Date:</span> {{orderDate}}</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

<p>We will notify you once your order is ready for shipping or pickup.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{storeUrl}}/account/orders" class="btn-primary">View Your Order</a>
</p>

<p>If you have any questions about your order, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br />
  <strong style="color: #D4AF37;">{{businessName}} Team</strong>
</p>
